Treasury balances at the FederalReserve rose on October 16 to 12.813 billion dlrs from 9.985billion dlrs on the previous business day, the Treasury said inits latest budget statement.    Balances in tax and loan note accounts rose to 28.398billion dlrs from 28.117 billion dlrs on the same respectivedays.    The Treasury's operating cash balance totaled 41.211billion dlrs on October 16 compared with 38.102 billion dlrs onOctober 15. Reuter&#3;